            . I keep a shop in <placeName id="t18150913-197-crimeloc1101">Well-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150913-197-crimeloc1101" type="placeName" value="Well-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18150913-197-crimeloc1101" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-197-off1099 t18150913-197-crimeloc1101"></join>. The prisoner and the deceased were standing against my door; they were differing about a reckoning. The deceased called the prisoner a rogue. The prisoner asked him would he say that again; he did, and Lowe knocked him down; immediately a one horse cart was coming by, and went over him.</p>
               <p>
            
