                     <interp inst="t18150913-197-person1751" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I belong to the London Hospital; and remember the body of the deceased<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181509130069"></xptr>being brought to me; he was then alive, but in a dying state, six of his ribs were fractured, and there was a wound on each lung; this occasioned his death.</p>
